Plot
Saugandh (1991) describes a widow anger women Ganga who wants to take revenge on the man Choudhary Sarang who killed her husband. She vows to get his daughter Chand married to her only son Shiva. So her strong and dare devil son, Shiva sets up his mind to wooing the pretty daughter of his father\'s murderer. But Chand is really affected and he forcibly kidnaps her and takes her to a secret place and tries to tame this wild horse. The end of the story deals whether he accepts and saves her wife or whether Ganga successful to avenge her husband's death?
